      <img src="images/slider/ergo_red_logo.jpg" />
<h1>Welcome to the ERGO Insurance branch in the UK!</h1>
<p>In April 2013, ERGO Insurance set up a new structure in UK operations by appointing D. Niemann, former Head of Munich Reâ€™s primary insurance activities in the UK &amp; Ireland and Chairman of Three Lions Underwriting Ltd (TLUL), as Head of the branch.</p>
<p>ERGO has taken the strategic decision to strengthen the presence in the UK &amp; Ireland and London market, based upon the very good experience and the potential, targeting industrial business in the UK &amp; Ireland alongside the take-over of TLUL, a London-based underwriting manager, wholly owned by Munich Re, which has successfully written commercial business for more than 13 years.</p>
<p>Based upon the very positive cooperation with ERGO in the past, the strategic decision was taken to transfer this commercial business intra-Group to ERGO as "best owner" to further progress the business.</p>
<p class="last"><a class="arrow" href="http://www.ergoinsurance.co.uk/ergo-in-the-uk-and-ireland.html">Read more...</a></p>

      
